We would like to draw your attention to the Theoretical Linguistics and=20
Applied Linguistics sections of the upcoming VARIETIES OF VOICE conference=
=20
in December in Leuven (Belgium), and warmly invite you to submit an=20
abstract before 14 September 2006. The plenary speakers are Prof. Suzanne=20
Kemmer (Rice University)  for the Linguistics section and Prof. Ken Hyland=
=20
